summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 59W, page 146, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Claremont Addition, Lots 1 thru 15, inclusive, Block 9, and Lots 17 thru 32, inclusive, Block 8, located on east and west side of Letitia Ave. between Adams St. and Genesee St. as Multiple Residence (RM) Zone.
